'''PlayStation Now'''是一個基於{{le|外海公司|Gaikai}}的[[雲端遊戲|雲端遊戲]]服務，用於向[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]、[[PlayStation_Vita_TV|PlayStation Vita TV]]和[[BRAVIA|BRAVIA電視]]提供[[PlayStation_(品牌)|PlayStation]]遊戲。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/7/5284504/sony-playstation-now-gaikai-based-streaming-service-ps-ps2-ps3 | title=Sony announces PlayStation Now, Gaikai-based streaming service | publisher=Polygon | date=7 January 2014 | accessdate=7 January 2014 | author=Sarkar, Samit | archive-date=2014-10-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010030424/http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/7/5284504/sony-playstation-now-gaikai-based-streaming-service-ps-ps2-ps3 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="platforms">{{cite web | url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/1/7/5284294/sony-announces-playstation-now-cloud-gaming | title=Sony announces PlayStation Now, its cloud gaming initative | publisher=The Verge | date=7 January 2014 | accessdate=7 January 2014 | author=Hollister, Sean | archive-date=2014-09-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140902233605/http://www.theverge.com/2014/1/7/5284294/sony-announces-playstation-now-cloud-gaming | dead-url=no }}</ref>該服務允許用戶付款，通過訂閱或按照單款遊戲售賣的計價的方式，獲得一段原PlayStation 3的遊戲作品訪問。該項目随后扩展到PS4作品，亦加入移植版本的[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]和[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]作品。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sony CES Keynote 2014 (PlayStation Now full segment)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LAZ7gksyF7Q&t=40m37s|work=Sony Electronics|accessdate=2014-09-06|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622223537/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LAZ7gksyF7Q&t=40m37s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/444296/ps4-games-in-the-pipeline-for-playstation-now | title = PS4 games in the pipeline for PlayStation Now | accessdate = 9 January 2014 | date = 9 January 2014 | publisher = CVG | first = Tom | last = Ivan | archive-date = 2014-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141017054648/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/444296/ps4-games-in-the-pipeline-for-playstation-now/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>若用戶使用非PlayStation設備要使用該服務，則需要[[DualShock|DualShock]] 3手柄支持，因為索尼認為這些遊戲是為其手柄而設計的，使用DualShock接入進行遊玩將會獲得最好的體驗，PlayStation品牌設備則可分別使用他們原來各自的遊戲控制器進行操作。<ref>{{cite web|last=Kubba|first=Sinan|title=Sony on controller requirements for PlayStation Now|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2014/01/08/sony-on-controller-requirements-for-playstation-now/|work=Joystiq|accessdate=12 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010024639/http://www.joystiq.com/2014/01/08/sony-on-controller-requirements-for-playstation-now/|archive-date=2014-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>索尼亦建議玩家配有5 Mbps的網絡連接以獲得他們認為的“良好表現”。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/09/playstation-now-requires-5mbs-connection| title = PlayStation Now Recommends 5Mb/s Connection| first = Luke| last = Karmali| date = 9 January 2014| accessdate = 10 January 2014| publisher = IGN| archive-date = 2014-10-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009203155/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/09/playstation-now-requires-5mbs-connection| dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 运作机制==
PS Now在其[[數據中心|數據中心]]使用經過修改的PS3設備，這樣的一台設備的一塊主板就擁有了等同於8台PS3主機的處理能力，它們被裝配在超薄型伺服器機櫃中。這樣做能夠獲得最好地利用機房空間，同時還能減少電力能耗。<ref>17 January 2014, [http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/17/5319370/report-sony-playstation-now-new-ps3-hardware Report: Sony develops new PS3 hardware for PlayStation Now] {{Wayback|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/17/5319370/report-sony-playstation-now-new-ps3-hardware |date=20141026154150 }}, Polygon</ref>根据其官方网站提供的信息到2014年10月为止已有超过150个PS3游戏可以公测方式供用户访问。
== 歷史 ==
PlayStation Now服務於2014年1月7日在[[國際消費電子展|2014年國際消費電子展]]（CES）上公開。<ref>{{cite web|last=Peckham|first=Matt|title=Sony Unveils ‘PlayStation Now’ Streaming Game Service at CES 2014|url=http://techland.time.com/2014/01/07/sony-unveils-playstation-now-streaming-game-service-at-ces-2014/|work=[[Time_(Magazine){{!}}Time|Time (Magazine){{!}}Time]]|accessdate=7 January 2014|archive-date=2014-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026014929/http://techland.time.com/2014/01/07/sony-unveils-playstation-now-streaming-game-service-at-ces-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IGN>{{cite web|last=Moriarty|first=Colin|title=Sony Reveals its Streaming Service: PlayStation Now|url=http://ign.com/articles/2014/01/07/sony-reveals-its-streaming-service-playstation-now|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=7 January 2014|archive-date=2014-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921183424/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/07/sony-reveals-its-streaming-service-playstation-now|dead-url=no}}</ref>索尼在CES上展示了《[[最後生還者|最後生還者]]》、《[[戰神：崛起|戰神：崛起]]》、《[[Puppeteer|Puppeteer]]》和《[[超能殺機：兩個靈魂|超能殺機：兩個靈魂]]》的演示。通過PS Now，以上PS3[[獨占遊戲|獨占遊戲]]都可以在BRAVIA電視和PlayStation Vita上玩到。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/spotify-netflix-and-now-playstation-streaming-finally-trickles-down-to-videogames | title=Spotify, Netflix and Now, PlayStation: streaming finally trickles down to videogames | work=Edge Online | date=8 January 2014 | accessdate=9 January 2014 | author=Neil Long | archive-date=2014-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017134806/http://www.edge-online.com/news/spotify-netflix-and-now-playstation-streaming-finally-trickles-down-to-videogames/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>PS Now的內部測試於1月28日在美國地區的PS3上開展，後於5月19日擴展至PS4。<ref name=IGN/><ref name=CNET>{{cite web|last=Reardon|first=Marguerite|title=Sony goes all-in on cloud with game, TV streaming|url=http://ces.cnet.com/8301-35284_1-57616786/sony-goes-all-in-on-cloud-with-game-tv-streaming/|work=[[CNET|CNET]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=7 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108011122/http://ces.cnet.com/8301-35284_1-57616786/sony-goes-all-in-on-cloud-with-game-tv-streaming/|archive-date=2014-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=PS4beta>{{cite web| url = http://blog.us.playstation.com/2014/05/19/playstation-now-ps4-private-beta-starts-tomorrow/#sf2993055| title = PlayStation Now: PS4 Private Beta Starts Tomorrow| first = Peter| last = Jamshidi| date = 19 May 2014| accessdate = 19 May 2014| publisher = ''PlayStation''| archive-date = 2014-10-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009075046/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2014/05/19/playstation-now-ps4-private-beta-starts-tomorrow/#sf2993055| dead-url = no}}</ref>PlayStation Now於2014年7月31日在[[美加地區|美加地區]]啟動PS4公測，9月18日啟動PS3公測，10月14日啟動PS Vita和PS Vita TV公測，此外2014年發布的特定型號BRAVIA電視亦將納入測試範圍。<ref name=PS4beta/><ref name=PS4official>{{cite web| url = http://us.playstation.com/playstationnow/| title = PlayStation Now| accessdate = 19 May 2014| publisher = ''PlayStation''| archive-date = 2014-07-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140702152136/http://us.playstation.com/playstationnow/| dead-url = no}}</ref>索尼電腦娛樂在[[Gamescom|Gamescom 2014]]上宣布PS Now將於2015年進入歐洲，英國將會成為第一個接入服務的歐洲區國家。<ref>Tom Ivan, [http://www.computerandvideogames.com/473995/playstation-now-coming-to-europe-in-2015/ PlayStation Now coming to Europe in 2015] {{Wayback|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/473995/playstation-now-coming-to-europe-in-2015/ |date=20140818142529 }}, 2014-08-12</ref>

* 2014年12月25日，PlayStation Now將廣大範圍到不同的電器品牌，三星將成爲第一個索尼之外的品牌，只有特定的智能電視支持PlayStation Now雲端遊戲服務，預計2015年的上半年在美國和加拿大地區推出。

*2015年1月13日，PlayStation Now推出订阅服务，PSN会员参与订阅计划，即可游玩库中所有游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=https://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/01/05/playstation-now-subscription-program-all-the-details/|title=PlayStation Now Subscription Program: All The Details|date=2015-01-05|author=Peter Jamshidi|website={{link-en|PlayStation Blog}}|language=en|archivedate=2015-01-05|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20150105142401/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2015/01/05/playstation-now-subscription-program-all-the-details/|access-date=2019-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该订阅机制先行在北美PSN展开。

* 2017年2月17日，索尼宣佈於同年8月15日終止PS3、PS Vita、PS TV、Sony Bravia及三星電視機等機種的PlayStation Now服務。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.us.playstation.com/2017/02/15/playstation-now-service-update/|title=PlayStation Now Service Update|date=2017-02-15|author=Brian Dunn|website={{link-en|PlayStation Blog}}|language=en|archivedate=2017-02-15|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20170215192134/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2017/02/15/playstation-now-service-update/|access-date=2017-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

* 2018年9月20日，PlayStation Now 允许下载库中的PS4游戏，和移植到PS4平台的PS2游戏于PlayStation4主机本地，不需联网即可游玩<ref>{{cite web|url=https://blog.us.playstation.com/2018/09/20/playstation-now-adds-downloading-of-ps4-ps2-games/|title=PlayStation Now Adds Downloading of PS4, PS2 Games|date=2018-09-20|author=Brian Dunn|website={{link-en|PlayStation Blog}}|language=en|archivedate=2019-06-12|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190612115850/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2018/09/20/playstation-now-adds-downloading-of-ps4-ps2-games/|access-date=2019-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

